Package: shinyhanzi
Title: Explore Chinese Characters with Animated Stroke Order and
    Dictionary Lookup
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Dylan", "Pieper", , "dylanpieper@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny application for exploring Chinese characters with
    animated stroke order, character decomposition, dictionary lookup with
    pinyin, English to Hanzi search, and frequency analysis. Includes
    reusable helper functions for Hanzi NLP backed by a DuckDB database.
